											<li class="date">NEXT MAXIMUS TOURNY STARTS SOON</li>
											<li class="tags"><a href="http://maps.google.it/maps?q=the+secret+theatre&hl=it&hq=the+secret+theatre&t=h&z=15" target="_blank">The Secret Theatre</a></li>
                                        </ul>
								</div>
									<p class="excerpt">
										Improvius Maximus challenges long-form improv teams from UCB, The PIT, The Magnet Theatre, and the best indie teams in NYC, to compete in Mighty Caesar's arena for laughs and for glory! Emperor Nero challenges the teams to complete hilarious tasks, or to improvise with outrageous restrictions imposed upon them. Citizens of Rome may sign up for a chance to compete before Caesar as part of a mixer team.  With Slave girl fetching beers and trusted hunky guard Foretourrus by Mighty Caesar's side, the future of comedy is Ancient Rome!
										<br/><br/>
										Free for improvisers from ANY comedy gladiator training ground / $5 citizens of Rome
