								</div>
									<p class="excerpt">
										Face Off takes you on a "non-stop comedy thrill ride" as it takes improvisation to A Whole 'Nother Level! This rockin' comedy show features live music and poetry, physical comedy, and plenty of audience interaction! Getting three suggestions from the audience at points throughout the show, Face Off demonstrates how all things, no matter how seemingly different, are actually connected. A Whole 'Nother Level is Face Off's premiere comedy show, starring Joe Tex, Jay Painter, and Eric Robinson, and is available for booking at colleges, festivals, corporate events, and custom designed improv and theatre workshop packages are available! 
