<!-- GOON RIVER SHOW START -->			  
				  <div id="post-1" class="blog-post">
							  <div class="title">
								<h2><a href="./article.html">Face Off Unlimited Presents Goon River</a></h2>
								</div>
								<a class="post-image" href="goonriver.html">
									<img height="200" width="200" alt="Thumb1" src="./images/goonriver.jpg" />
								</a>
								<div class="post-detail">
								  <div class="post-info">
										<ul>
											<li class="date">Next show: TBA</li>
											<li class="tags">Location: TBA</li>
										</ul>
								  </div>
									<p class="excerpt">
								   Adapted from a classic improvisation exorcise, Face Off has created a new type of theatre experience, where audience members are literally surrounded by the story. By turning out the lights and removing the visual aspects of the experience, the story telling becomes personal to each theatre goer's imagination. With the actors seated throughout the audience, the listener is immersed into the world woven by Face Off's master improvised story tellers that is unique to each performance.  Check back here to find out when you can take a trip down to the All-American town, GOON RIVER!</p>
									<div style="width:500px ; float:left"> <a href="goonriver.html"><img src="images/more_button.png" width="89" height="33" alt="Read More" /></a><!-- Buy Tickets link <a href="https://web.ovationtix.com/trs/pe/9756145" target="_blank"><img src="images/buy_ticketssmall.png" width="89" height="33" alt="Buy Tickets" /></a>--></div>												
