<!-- FNFO SHOW START -->  
                                <div id="post-5" class="blog-post">
								<div class="title">
									<h2><a href="#">Friday Night Face Off</a></h2>
									
								</div>
								<a class="post-image" href="fnfo.html">
									<img height="200" width="200" alt="Thumb1" src="./images/shows_fnfo.png" />
								</a>
							  <div class="post-detail">
								  <div class="post-info">
										<ul>
											<li class="date">Every Friday at 10:30 PM</li>
											<li class="tags"><a href="http://maps.google.it/maps?q=%22Theatre+Three%22+new+york&ll=41.286062,-73.042603&spn=2.340294,5.410767&fb=1&gl=it&hq=%22Theatre+Three%22+new+york&hnear=%22Theatre+Three%22+new+york&cid=0,0,14276761080891812889&t=h&z=8&iwloc=A" title="Theatre Three" target="_blank">Theatre Three</a></li>
										</ul>
								</div>
									<p class="excerpt">
										Friday Night Face Off is the longest running professional improv comedy show in Long Island History! The New York Times calls it "A Late Night Hit!" and Newsday crowns FNFO "the Granddaddy of LI Improv!" Face Off Unlimited founders Jay Painter and Eric Robinson co-created the show a decade ago. You can see the current cast of FNFO every Friday night at Theatre Three in Port Jefferson, NY. Visit the shows website fridaynightfaceoff.com to learn more!
									</p>
<div style="width:500px ; float:left"> <a href="fnfo.html"><img src="images/more_button.png" width="89" height="33" alt="Read More" /></a></div>												
